import { AppBar, Button, Tab, Tabs, Tooltip, Typography } from "@mui/material"
function navBar() {
  return (
    <>
      <AppBar>
        <Tooltip>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{float:"left"}}>LOGO</Typography>
            <Tabs sx={{float:"right"}}>
                <Tab label='Home'/>
                <Tab label='About'/>
                <Tab label='Contact'/>

            </Tabs>
            <Button variant="contained" sx={{float:"right",marginTop:'5px'}}>Login</Button>
        </Tooltip>
      </AppBar>
    </>
  )
}

export default navBar
